<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="25200000t" end="35600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0"><font face="DFGKaisho-Bd" size="32" color="#e0e0e0">{\an8}あっどっこい</font></p>
<p begin="25200000t" end="35600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1"><font face="方正楷体_GBK" size="34" color="#e0e0e0"><b>啊嘿呀</b></font></p>
<p begin="107400000t" end="116500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2"><font face="DFGKaisho-Bd" size="32" color="#e0e0e0">{\an8}あっほいっしゅ</font></p>
<p begin="107400000t" end="116500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3"><font face="方正楷体_GBK" size="34" color="#e0e0e0"><b>啊嘿哟</b></font></p>
<p begin="194500000t" end="235400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4"><font face="DFGKaisho-Bd" size="32" color="#e0e0e0">{\an8}見渡せば　一面　白金の世界に</font></p>
<p begin="194500000t" end="235400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5"><font face="方正楷体_GBK" size="34" color="#e0e0e0"><b>极目远眺  一眼望去尽是白金的世界</b></font></p>
<p begin="236600000t" end="275900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6"><font face="DFGKaisho-Bd" size="32" color="#e0e0e0">{\an8}一歩だけ踏み出して</font></p>
<p begin="236600000t" end="275900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7"><font face="方正楷体_GBK" size="34" color="#e0e0e0"><b>就向前踏出这一步吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="277100000t" end="297100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8"><font face="DFGKaisho-Bd" size="32" color="#e0e0e0">{\an8}いつまでも　止まらない</font></p>
<p begin="277100000t" end="297100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9"><font face="方正楷体_GBK" size="34" color="#e0e0e0"><b>无论何时  永不停步</b></font></p>
<p begin="298000000t" end="317100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10"><font face="DFGKaisho-Bd" size="32" color="#e0e0e0">{\an8}この胸の　トキメキで</font></p>
<p begin="298000000t" end="317100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11"><font face="方正楷体_GBK" size="34" color="#e0e0e0"><b>用心中的那份悸动</b></font></p>
<p begin="318400000t" end="353400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12"><font face="DFGKaisho-Bd" size="32" color="#e0e0e0">{\an8}一緒に踊ろう</font></p>
<p begin="318400000t" end="353400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13"><font face="方正楷体_GBK" size="34" color="#e0e0e0"><b>和你一起舞动吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="363000000t" end="408900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14"><font face="DFGKaisho-Bd" size="32" color="#e0e0e0">{\an8}君の背中であの日見つけた月が</font></p>
<p begin="363000000t" end="408900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15"><font face="方正楷体_GBK" size="34" color="#e0e0e0"><b>那天在你的背上所看到的月亮</b></font></p>
<p begin="420600000t" end="481500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16"><font face="DFGKaisho-Bd" size="32" color="#e0e0e0">{\an8}今日も　ミラーボールみたいに　夜空で</font></p>
<p begin="420600000t" end="481500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17"><font face="方正楷体_GBK" size="34" color="#e0e0e0"><b>现在也如玻璃球一样在夜空中</b></font></p>
<p begin="482300000t" end="543200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18"><font face="DFGKaisho-Bd" size="32" color="#e0e0e0">{\an8}キラリ　チラリ　輝いてる</font></p>
<p begin="482300000t" end="543200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19"><font face="方正楷体_GBK" size="34" color="#e0e0e0"><b>闪闪亮亮地  发着光</b></font></p>
<p begin="560700000t" end="603700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20"><font face="DFGKaisho-Bd" size="32" color="#e0e0e0">{\an8}変わってくもの　変わらないもの</font></p>
<p begin="560700000t" end="603700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21"><font face="方正楷体_GBK" size="34" color="#e0e0e0"><b>渐渐改变的东西  一成不变的东西</b></font></p>
<p begin="605800000t" end="642500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22"><font face="DFGKaisho-Bd" size="32" color="#e0e0e0">{\an8}飽きっぽいわたしが</font></p>
<p begin="605800000t" end="642500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23"><font face="方正楷体_GBK" size="34" color="#e0e0e0"><b>容易厌倦的我</b></font></p>
<p begin="644100000t" end="685800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24"><font face="DFGKaisho-Bd" size="32" color="#e0e0e0">{\an8}初めて知った　この永遠を</font></p>
<p begin="644100000t" end="685800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25"><font face="方正楷体_GBK" size="34" color="#e0e0e0"><b>用这初次知道的永恒</b></font></p>
<p begin="687500000t" end="727600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26"><font face="DFGKaisho-Bd" size="32" color="#e0e0e0">{\an8}君に誓うよ</font></p>
<p begin="687500000t" end="727600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27"><font face="方正楷体_GBK" size="34" color="#e0e0e0"><b>与你交换誓言</b></font></p>
<p begin="729200000t" end="768400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28"><font face="DFGKaisho-Bd" size="32" color="#e0e0e0">{\an8}プラチナ　うれしいのに</font></p>
<p begin="729200000t" end="768400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29"><font face="方正楷体_GBK" size="34" color="#e0e0e0"><b><font face="Comic Sans MS"></font></b>Platinum</font><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">  明明应该高兴的</font></p>
<p begin="770100000t" end="810600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30"><font face="DFGKaisho-Bd" size="32" color="#e0e0e0">{\an8}プラチナ　切なくなって</font></p>
<p begin="770100000t" end="810600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31"><font face="方正楷体_GBK" size="34" color="#e0e0e0"><b><font face="Comic Sans MS"></font></b>Platinum</font><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">  但却变得忧郁了</font></p>
<p begin="811800000t" end="860600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32"><font face="DFGKaisho-Bd" size="32" color="#e0e0e0">{\an8}プラチナ　涙が出ちゃうのはなんで</font></p>
<p begin="811800000t" end="860600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33"><font face="方正楷体_GBK" size="34" color="#e0e0e0"><b><font face="Comic Sans MS"></font></b>Platinum<font face="方正楷体_GBK"><b>  为何会流下泪水</b></font></font></p>
<p begin="861900000t" end="890600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34"><font face="DFGKaisho-Bd" size="32" color="#e0e0e0">{\an8}どうしてディスコティック</font></p>
<p begin="861900000t" end="890600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35"><font face="方正楷体_GBK" size="34" color="#e0e0e0"><b>为什么会如此地迪斯风</b></font></p>
<p begin="910700000t" end="950700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33"><b>{\an8}<font size="45">历与茶</font></b></font></p>
<p begin="910700000t" end="950700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="36"><b>{\an8}本字幕仅供交流试看之用，如您喜欢本作品，请支持购买正版。<br />若因私自散布传播造成法律及相关一切问题，华盟字幕社概不负责。</b></font></p>
<p begin="950700000t" end="980700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="36"><b>{\an8}翻译：痛爱的飞鱼；后期：snow。</b></font></p>
<p begin="965700000t" end="980700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">{\an2}<font size="45">十月</font></font></p>
<p begin="1042000000t" end="1068700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哥哥  你相信有妖怪吗？</font></p>
<p begin="1080400000t" end="1122500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">妖怪？什么意思？你是不是从千石那儿听说了什么？</font></p>
<p begin="1125900000t" end="1167600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯？这里为什么要提抚子的名字？</font></p>
<p begin="1170500000t" end="1198900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哥哥说的话有时候让人莫名其妙的</font></p>
<p begin="1200900000t" end="1213900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不  没什么</font></p>
<p begin="1220500000t" end="1242200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">话说你为什么突然问关于妖怪的问题？</font></p>
<p begin="1245600000t" end="1278900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">难道你是想说茶道室里有妖怪出没？</font></p>
<p begin="1280600000t" end="1306000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">没错就是这样  哥哥真是明白人</font></p>
<p begin="1301500000t" end="1311500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="23"><b>{\an8}<font face="方正准圆_GBK"><font size="33">居然蒙对了</font></font></b></font></p>
<p begin="1324400000t" end="1369000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">正确来说应该是「茶道室里曾经有妖怪出没」</font></p>
<p begin="1371500000t" end="1401600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">曾经有？这是什么意思？</font></p>
<p begin="1405700000t" end="1438300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你是说在茶道室里发现了它曾经存在的痕迹吗？</font></p>
<p begin="1440300000t" end="1484100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">也很难说是有什么痕迹</font></p>
<p begin="1484100000t" end="1521700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">并没有什么客观证据可以证明那孩子曾经存在</font></p>
<p begin="1524200000t" end="1530400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那孩子？</font></p>
<p begin="1530400000t" end="1545500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="23"><b>{\an8}<font face="方正准圆_GBK"><font size="33">这用词具体得有些奇怪</font></font></b></font></p>
<p begin="1547500000t" end="1568800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">月火  我来给你讲讲道理</font></p>
<p begin="1571300000t" end="1608000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">既然没有证据  就说明妖怪并不存在</font></p>
<p begin="1610500000t" end="1630500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">好了  这次的故事就这样讲完了</font></p>
<p begin="1633900000t" end="1665600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">接下来的时间就全用来闲聊好了</font></p>
<p begin="1725200000t" end="1761900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我是来和你商量的  才不要和你闲聊呢</font></p>
<p begin="1763600000t" end="1778600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">明白了明白了</font></p>
<p begin="1780300000t" end="1811100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">吁吁  我明白了  你快把那圆珠笔收起来</font></p>
<p begin="1812000000t" end="1852800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">收起来？你是让我把这三色圆珠笔的哪个颜色收起来呢？</font></p>
<p begin="1854500000t" end="1880400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">全收起来  红色蓝色黑色全部</font></p>
<p begin="1881600000t" end="1900400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">话说  到底是怎么回事？</font></p>
<p begin="1903300000t" end="1937900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你说茶道室里曾经有妖怪出没  又说没有证据</font></p>
<p begin="1941700000t" end="1965500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我刚才不就是这么说的嘛  你没听见吗？</font></p>
<p begin="1967500000t" end="2013400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">让我猜一下  是不是你已经证明了妖怪不存在于现在的时间点？</font></p>
<p begin="2015900000t" end="2035900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哇  你怎么知道的？</font></p>
<p begin="2042200000t" end="2068900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">事情的经过大概是这样的</font></p>
<p begin="2074700000t" end="2106000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">有传言称茶道部的活动室里有幽灵出没</font></p>
<p begin="2109400000t" end="2141000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">月火或许不是以Fire Sister的成员</font></p>
<p begin="2141000000t" end="2178600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">而是以阿良良木月火个人的名义前去对这个传言进行调查</font></p>
<p begin="2183600000t" end="2200300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">然后事情便解决了</font></p>
<p begin="2203600000t" end="2226600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我该怎么办啊？哥哥</font></p>
<p begin="2229100000t" end="2239900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯？什么怎么办？</font></p>
<p begin="2242000000t" end="2319100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我是说…我已经有理有据地证明了妖怪现在并不存在</font></p>
<p begin="2319100000t" end="2351700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">但是却没有一个人相信我</font></p>
<p begin="2351700000t" end="2385900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">比起我大家更相信妖怪</font></p>
<p begin="2418800000t" end="2440500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">茶道部一共有七个人</font></p>
<p begin="2440500000t" end="2535600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45"><font size="38">传言有第八个成员存在的依据  目击报告和状况证明也都被我有理有据地一一证伪</font></font></p>
<p begin="2539800000t" end="2550600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">有理有据地</font></p>
<p begin="2556000000t" end="2587300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不要故意强调「有理有据」  这样听起来反倒有些可以了</font></p>
<p begin="2587300000t" end="2604800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">{\an1}说我可疑也太失礼了吧</font></p>
<p begin="2604800000t" end="2648600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我可是费了千辛万苦才否定了第八个成员的存在</font></p>
<p begin="2648600000t" end="2673700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">可大家却都对我这样说</font></p>
<p begin="2673700000t" end="2701200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">「也有可能是这样吧  算了不要计较了」</font></p>
<p begin="2701200000t" end="2732500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">「月火说的也可能是对的」</font></p>
<p begin="2732500000t" end="2756200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">「虽然理论上可能是这样没错」</font></p>
<p begin="2756200000t" end="2790000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">「但说不定第八个成员也真的存在呢」</font></p>
<p begin="2792100000t" end="2824200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">她们都这么说  传言根本就没法消灭！</font></p>
<p begin="2864700000t" end="2897200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你怎么看？哥哥  你觉得我该怎么办啊？</font></p>
<p begin="2899300000t" end="2911000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你问我我怎么知道</font></p>
<p begin="2913100000t" end="2938100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你觉得在这种情况下该怎么办？</font></p>
