<p begin="6238100000t" end="6258500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">好的  那我就假装上当好了</font></p>
<p begin="6258500000t" end="6272300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">假装被她们骗了</font></p>
<p begin="6272300000t" end="6289800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就让她们和稀泥好了</font></p>
<p begin="6297300000t" end="6318600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我把这件事告诉神原之后</font></p>
<p begin="6324800000t" end="6361500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯  茶道部员和阿良良木学长</font></p>
<p begin="6361500000t" end="6402800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">月火妹妹她究竟是上了谁的当呢？</font></p>
<p begin="6605900000t" end="6661400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198"><font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">将烦恼踢开  石头顺势滚落</font></p>
<p begin="6605900000t" end="6661400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}悩み 蹴飛ばして石が転がってく</font></p>
<p begin="6661800000t" end="6719000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200"><font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">稍加掩饰的  是四月的事情</font></p>
<p begin="6661800000t" end="6719000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}少し 誤魔化した あれは四月のこと</font></p>
<p begin="6719000000t" end="6773200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202"><font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">曾经的我们都是好奇心旺盛的开朗孩子</font></p>
<p begin="6719000000t" end="6773200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}好奇心旺盛で 明るい子供でした</font></p>
<p begin="6773600000t" end="6833200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204"><font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">在背后推着我们的是那一天开始的冒险</font></p>
<p begin="6773600000t" end="6833200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}背中押したのは あの日からの冒險</font></p>
<p begin="6833200000t" end="6890400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206"><font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">追寻着那些不出格的热度</font></p>
<p begin="6833200000t" end="6890400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}はみ出せない熱を追いに行って</font></p>
<p begin="6890800000t" end="6944600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208"><font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">到处闲逛</font></p>
<p begin="6890800000t" end="6944600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}道草をしよう</font></p>
<p begin="6963400000t" end="7020500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210"><font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">将重要的梦想放进箱子</font></p>
<p begin="6963400000t" end="7020500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}箱に乗せ 大切な夢</font></p>
<p begin="7020500000t" end="7076800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212"><font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">踩起脚踏板  将它带到远方</font></p>
<p begin="7020500000t" end="7076800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}ペダル回し 遠くまで さぁ 持ち出そう</font></p>
<p begin="7076800000t" end="7130600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214"><font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">传说中我们的未来</font></p>
<p begin="7076800000t" end="7130600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}噂した 僕の未来は</font></p>
<p begin="7131000000t" end="7167700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216"><font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">有着我们各自的模样</font></p>
<p begin="7131000000t" end="7167700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}個々人の伸びる丈に</font></p>
<p begin="7167700000t" end="7209900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218"><font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">怎么说也听不懂</font></p>
<p begin="7167700000t" end="7209900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}聞いてもわからない</font></p>
<p begin="7210300000t" end="7269900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220"><font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">听不懂啊听不懂</font></p>
<p begin="7210300000t" end="7269900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}わからない わからない</font></p>
</div>
